appraw is a tool for patching .desktop files to make apps be launched
via fsoraw (to prevent automatic screen dimming and suspending).

It can be used in various distribution enhancing scripts or just to
make freshly installed app fsoraw-enabled.

See 'appraw --help' for details.

Example usage:

  appraw -i CPU,Display tangogps
  appraw -i Display tangogps
  appraw -d mokomaze
  appraw -r mokomaze

